### HYMN LI

#### A sacrificial formula

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1905101">1</span></span>Undisturbed
am I, undisturbed is my soul, undisturbed mine  
   eye, undisturbed mine ear, undisturbed is mine in-breathing,  
   undisturbed mine out-breathing, undisturbed my diffusive-  
   breath, undisturbed the whole of me.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1905102">2</span></span>Under the
impulse of the God Savitar, sent forth from the arms-  
   of the Asvins and both hands of Pūshan I have taken thee.

